thread.title: BRIEF-Meridia Real Estate III FY Operational Result At 12.2 Mln Euros

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Meridia Real Estate III FY Operational Result At 12.2 Mln Euros
text:
Feb 23 (Reuters) - Meridia Real Estate III SOCIMI SA :
* ON THURSDAY REPORTED FY NET TURNOVER OF 8.7 MILLION EUROS
* FY OPERATIONAL RESULT AND PROVISIONAL RESULT FOR THE YEAR AT 12.2 MILLION EUROS
* NET ASSET VALUE 118.5 MILLION EUROS AT END-DEC.
Source text: bit.ly/2EKY2g9
